    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"jw4-02-after.jpg\" width=\"1416\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542218994/jw4-02-after.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1756252706231&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1416&amp;height=593\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542218994/jw4-02-after.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1756252706231&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"805\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"572915732\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"jw4-02-after.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542218994\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"8726bb69-a31e-4a9d-99e1-7294f7dc2baa\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542218994/jw4-02-after.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1756252706231&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1920&amp;height=805 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542218994/jw4-02-after.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1756252706231&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1416&amp;height=593 1x\"></span><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">MaterialX Lama is a state of the art material layering system developed at Industrial Light &amp; Magic that introduces a modular approach to building material networks and includes recent shading R&amp;D work on energy conservation and dispersion. </span></p><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">The MaterialX Lama project represents ongoing R&amp;D into materials at ILM, and represents one facet of the larger MaterialX project.  </span><br/></p><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">MaterialX Lama node composition also offers a simpler built-in mechanism for energy conservation and other properties, because of its fundamental focus on layering of physically based responses.</span></p><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">MaterialX Lama is battle-tested at ILM and RenderMan will be able to take advantage of ongoing work as it evolves.</span></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"256\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542218994/materialx-lama-icon.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330542599&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542218994/materialx-lama-icon.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330542599&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"256\" data-width=\"256\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219006\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"materialx-lama-icon.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542218994\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"83b05612-112d-470b-a3d2-e4c4f6e66b5f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542218994/materialx-lama-icon.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330542599&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542218994/materialx-lama-icon.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330542599&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 1x\"></span><ul class=\"childpages-macro con